98
00:15:13,420 --> 00:15:20,260
 I ljudi kažu, CGPT me bolje razumije od moje, sad ću karikirati, od moje obitelji.

99
00:15:20,260 --> 00:15:20,920
 Zanimljivo.

100
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,200
